---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Vivek.dev" description="About Vivek.dev.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl py-6 sm:py-12">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-blue-700 uppercase">About</p>
    <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-balance sm:text-5xl">A little about me.</h1>
    <div class="mt-9 space-y-6 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
      <p>I'm a software engineer with over 15 years of experience building Java-based applications and distributed systems. My primary focus is on backend engineering, Spring Boot, Kubernetes, and cloud-native architectures.</p>
      <p>I enjoy understanding how systems work beneath the surface. Outside of day-to-day development, I create technical content and continuously explore modern software engineering practices.</p>
      <p>This site is where I share practical articles, experiments, and lessons learned while building reliable, scalable software.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
